  <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#broughtAbout">
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#Situation"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Identifies a gufo:Situation that is brought about by the gufo:Event.

Guizzardi et al. (2013) included a notion of "brings-about" that related events to a single ("maximal") situation, embodying all the effects of the event at the time it ends. This implementation of gufo:broughtAbout diverges from "brings-about" in that work because gufo:broughtAbout can be used to relate events to more than one gufo:Situation. Each gufo:Situation identified through gufo:broughtAbout should be understood as an (improper) part of the maximal situation.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#Event"/>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">broughtAbout</rdfs:label>
  </owl:ObjectProperty>
